DOMAIN,api-access.pangolin-sdk-toutiao2.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pangolin-sdk-toutiao.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pangolin-sdk-toutiao-b.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pangolin-sdk-toutiao1.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pangolin-sdk-toutiao2.com,REJECT-DROP
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pangle.io,REJECT-DROP

